Version 2.0
===========
* Added the option of k points to be modified into loo and moo (and parent functions to pass down)
* Added arguments to main functions to allow the user to pick which subset of points are starting points (in conjunction with k sequential) to modify.  This includes "all" which gives the previous behaviour, "random" (uniform), "stratified" (by segment), or a vector of indices.

Version 1.0.1
=============
* Changed itemize to describe in InfluenceMap.Rd - CRAN check
* Removed generic use of influence(model,...) from usage area in influence-methods.Rd - CRAN check
* Updated format of NEWS to comply with new CRAN checks
* Updated references throughout to JCGS citation instead of ArXiV

Version 1.0
===========
* First CRAN release

